    ('BUKD-L 578', 'MANAGING CYBER RISKS IN THE GLOBAL MARKETPLACE: LEGAL, ETHICAL & POLICY PERSPECTIVES', '10844', 'Closed', 'M Monday 6:00 PM–7:15 PM', 'WB WEB', 'Scott Shackelford', 0, NULL, 'Discussion', '3', 'WEB-BASED CLASS', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'The primary aim of the course is to provide students with a basic working knowledge of cybersecurity law and policy, focusing on the United States but put in a global perspective.', ARRAY['Kelley Direct Program Bloomington'], NULL),
